  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support Greek farmers,Shepherdog breeds &amp; wildlife</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Shepherd dogs are the most important measure for the livestock breeders to protect their flock from bears and wolves. In Greece the breeders do not receive subsidies for the acquisition and raise of a shepherd dog. So Callisto founded a Shepherd Dogs Network to donate puppies to breeders that face losses from large carnivores. This way the network contributes to the conservation of the Greek shepherd dog breeds and protects the large carnivores by improving their coexistence with the farmers.</narrative>
  </description>
